reviews.text: It's hard to imagine roles that would be worse than Osama, but you surpassed them in this. We have never eaten such disgusting rolls in our lives. Fish with bones, eel is a separate matter; in normal deliveries these parts of the eel are considered food waste, but not with you. (I’ll show you in the photo), the salmon was impossible to chew, the shrimp tasted like it was swimming in mud. The only roll that was possible to eat was a roll with a crab stick; everything else went into the trash. The cheese is sour, the cucumber has skin, all the rolls fall apart. If I could give 0 stars, I would give 0.

Below is my first review, where I gave 5 stars and praised this place a year ago. The photo is also from that time.
BUT: NOT EVERYTHING is like that now! That's why she took the star.

Let me explain:

1. Made an order.
They brought roles and...money. As I later understood - there is no money for a role that is not available. No one called to warn. They just deposited money. And for that, thank you. It's not exactly bad, but it's 2 minutes to call and clarify. Communication and politeness is also the key to keep people coming back to you! I was already ready to run and give the taxi driver money, because I thought it was his. It's good that I looked at the order first and made a logical chain. I understand that there may be no ingredients and I am fine with that, but it would be nice if they called and warned. :)
2. Tom Yum…Sorry, but this is a parody. It tastes sour. Shitaki rubber. The broth is not at all like in Tom Yum... here it's just like water and chili. Didn't finish. Very strange taste, so I don't recommend it if you really want this particular soup. I will definitely not order here again.
3. Baked roll: since when is there regular grated cheese? The feeling of eating a sandwich. This roll used to melt in the mouth. And now this cheese under the cap is still unbaked. Maybe it was there before, but then it was definitely baked so that all the cheese melted and there was not a single piece of ordinary cheese. Before, it seemed that there was some cheese cream mass. Now it's not like that at all.
4. The packaging is now plastic. There used to be paper. Purely from the point of view of ecology, I am more in favor of paper, but I understand that the war may not be possible to order such packaging, or the economy. Here you can somehow find an explanation. Therefore, approx.
5. The other rolls were delicious. Delivery is not very long. But in general, the impression has deteriorated somewhat. That's why I took one star.
6. FINALLY the operator speaks Ukrainian!! +

Will I order again? I allow But definitely not baked rolls and not that yam.
________________

I really liked the roles. Delicious. fresh Portions correspond to their price. Definitely recommend and will order again!

They delivered very quickly, and despite the fact that there was no courier function at the moment, they resolved this issue and delivered the sushi. The girl brought the sushi wearing a mask and gloves, which is very important given the current situation! The sushi is incredibly tasty, a lot of fish, juicy! I really recommend it! I was satisfied, even despite my picky taste for little things!

I will write a review here, and then on Instagram, if the reviews are negative, their cunning admin will delete them. They made a pre-order and paid immediately because they can’t do anything else, they ordered for 19:00, the delivery arrived at 21:45 and that’s half the trouble, they wanted to call to find out the status of the order, for an hour and a half no one picked up the phone because “all operators are busy” then almost at 22:00 a taxi arrives with an order, the driver says that you have to pay for the delivery, although it should be free, because the order is more than a thousand and was within the radius of their delivery
I definitely do not advise!

These are the best rolls I've tried. We have been ordering for many years (Kryukiv region, since the opening of the establishment here), we are very satisfied, not a single negative experience - always fast, high-quality, tasty, service at the highest level. Really big in size, lots of toppings, not just rice like sometimes in other places. It's also beautifully decorated - today they put rolls on beautiful leaves, I didn't take a photo, because it's so appetizing that I couldn't resist tasting this delicacy. Thank you!
The review is not paid for - it is a sincere confession of love for this establishment.
